						<div class="postbody">The only difference with Nintendulator is about clocking the PPU <em>after</em> the CPU cycle. In my emulator, I just follow what should be. If $2002 is read 1 PPU cycle before VBlank, $2002:$80 is NOT set; hence, NMIs are not triggered too.</div>

